                     <interp inst="t17310428-24-off118" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing a Gold-Watch, value 20 l. a Gold-Ring set with Diamonds, several pieces of Plate, &amp;c
            </rs>. the Goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17310428-24-victim130" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Keen 
                  <interp inst="t17310428-24-victim130" type="surname" value="Keen"></interp>
